/// | [032..064) | recipient | bytes32 | 32    | Recipient address on destination chain |
/// | [064..096) | tips      | uint256 | 32    | Encoded tips paid on origin chain      |
/// | [096..116) | request   | uint160 | 20    | Encoded request for message execution  |
